ησε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"λε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"λε\">λε</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.5)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Katherine Backler</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>❦<span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"Δαίμοσιν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δαιμόνιος\">Δ</span>❦<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\"><span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ῥωμάνα\"><span data-text=\"Ῥωμάνα\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Ῥωμάνα\">ΡΩΜΑΝΑ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔ\n                    τη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">Ε<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"λε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"λε\">ΛΕ</span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>❦&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"Δαίμοσιν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δαιμόνιος\">ΔΑΙΜΟΣΙΝ</span><span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Ῥωμάνα\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Ῥωμάνα\">ΡΩΜΑΝΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"λε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"λε\">ΛΕ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003511_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003511_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003511.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003511-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based upon Bitto 2001 and photograph.</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-5532-9917\">Katherine Backler</a></p>  <p>To the divine spirits. Klodia Romana lived 35 years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1916 134 fig.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701</a>  </li><li> Bitto 2001 4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Somewhat irregular letters, tending to cursive (e.g. mu), and often leaning to the left; omega, sigma and epislon all lunate in form; theta a circle with an unconnected central bar; triangular letters tend to have a slightly extended top stroke.</p> Lines 1-4  22-28  Line 5  30  Interlineation lines 1 to 5  10-13  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
